Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}假裝不感興趣的維納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:34.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}迷路  幻想  Highway  Seek your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:38.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Inside Noside  是否已經欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:41.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}妄想無論何時都甜如蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:45.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Outside Noside  如果這樣還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:46.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\fs25\pos(685,48)}肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:46.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}那就暴露『本能』吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}來吧  Naked Dive!  釋放情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}對真實的你一探究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:56.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}沒錯  Naked Dive!  衝動的Myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}只要好奇心不言放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Making your world!!　 忘我地吶喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Changing your world!!  沒有所謂的極限
